            <ab>P. L. Bat. 25 41 (English)

                    Donatus (?) to the strategoi of the Arsinoite nome: greetings.
                    As my care extends to all - - - not only with regard to the just character in - - - (because of my) humanity, I have judged it necessary to publish what I have said during the conventus in the records, by way of letter as well.</ab>
